Languagelayer,serves,as,a,platform,for,detecting,the,structural,textual,and,semantic,characteristics,of,different,languages,It,is,a,fully,documented,AI,based,version,that,operates,as,a,simple,REST,API,capable,of,analyzing,more,than,languages,The,free,API,conveys,responses,in,JSON,format,and,requires,access,key,to,authenticate,and,post,requests